Seaplanes, sometimes called ''flying boats'', were used during WW2. They were utilized in various tasks from anti-submarine patrol to air-sea rescue and [[Combat/Artillery Spotting|artillery spotting]] for battleships.
*Green : Outstanding

*Yellow : Above average
